es.\\\",\n      \\\"what_not_to_copy\\\": \\\"Do not clone proprietary imagery, layouts, or badge systems from private references.\\\"\n    },\n    {\n      \\\"id\\\": \\\"obs-006\\\",\n      \\\"evidence\\\": [\n        \\\"apple-hig-research and behavioral-ux-research: access is source-limited; both files emphasize accessibility and emotional safety in high-pressure screens.\\\"\n      ],\n      \\\"what_to_adapt\\\": \\\"Preserve interruption-safe controls and large, discoverable actions in active wake mode.\\\",\n      \\\"what_not_to_copy\\\": \\\"Do not add decorative motion or custom interactions that reduce accessibility signal strength.\\\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \\\"screen_types\\\": [\n    \\\"onboarding\\\",\n    \\\"home\\\",\n    \\\"auth\\\",\n    \\\"create_edit\\\",\n    \\\"active_task\\\",\n    \\\"completion\\\",\n    \\\"history_streaks\\\",\n    \\\"profile_settings\\\",\n    \\\"paywall_subscription\\\"\n  ],\n  \\\"raw_assets\\\": [\n    {\n      \\\"path\\\": \\\".workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/research/existing-app-intake.md\\\",\n      \\\"source\\\": \\\"existing_app_intake\\\",\n      \\\"private_only\\\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \\\"path\\\": \\\".workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/research/reference-gap-analysis.json\\\",\n      \\\"source\\\": \\\"reference_gap_analysis\\\",\n      \\\"private_only\\\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \\\"path\\\": \\\".workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/research/competitor-flows.md\\\",\n      \\\"source\\\": \\\"competitor_flows\\\",\n      \\\"private_only\\\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \\\"path\\\": \\\".workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/research/app-store-review-mining.md\\\",\n      \\\"source\\\": \\\"app_store_review\\\",\n      \\\"private_only\\\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \\\"path\\\": \\\".workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/research/mobbin-mcp-research.md\\\",\n      \\\"source\\\": \\\"mobbin_fallback\\\",\n      \\\"private_only\\\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \\\"path\\\": \\\".workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/res